 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EScratch Hard is a shopping companion app that allows users to browse and discover in-store sales and promotions, save coupons, and share their experience with others.  The purpose is for users to be able to discover great offers from name brand retailers on whatever they\u0026#8217;re out shopping for, wherever they are, whenever they want them.  (And to have fun doing so!) \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EScratch Hard is reinventing the retailer experience by leveraging what works with online shopping, with the best parts of in-store shopping \u2013 touching, feeling, trying on.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EWe feel passionately that categories of shopping, like fashion, home d\u00e9cor simply do not hit their full potential online.  It is a pastime \u2013 people enjoy shopping!  Scratch Hard makes this activity more fun, more productive, more interesting.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EWHO NEEDS SCRATCH HARD?\nANY MOBILE USER out shopping for clothing, electronics, home goods, beauty/cosmetics, kids gear, pet stuff, automotive supplies, sporting goods \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThose that have an IMMEDIATE NEED. Scratch Hard finds that item they are looking for. \u201cI need a belt for this meeting!\u201d \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EIMPULSE BUYERS who will respond to location-based alerts and see a promotion at the perfect moment\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EACTIVE SHOPPERS who have been trained to ignore the daily flood ofemail offers  \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EPRACTICAL SHOPPERS, such as busy parents, who like to pre-plan their shopping route based on offers that appeal to them\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EVISITORS AND VACATIONERS who are unfamiliar with the retail landscape outside their home cities  \u003C/p\u003E",
